00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:22.320
Ganoon ba?

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:26.360
Hanapin ang lugar!

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:26.890
Oo, sir.

00:04:34.280 --> 00:04:35.280
